"mediator" who is not needed at all in the solution of the 
question during his foreign trip. This shows well how 
persistently the puppets are trying to put a spoke in the wheel 
of the DPRK-U.S. talks again. 
  Facts clearly prove that the Kim Yong-sam group is, indeed, 
a 
