headine] 
  [Text] Pyongyang, May 28 (KCNA) -- The U.S. imperialists' 
wild ambition to dominate Asia can never be realized, stresses 
NODONG SINMUN in a signed article today. 
  The United States is trying to break up and stifle socialist 
countries in Asia with its "peaceful transition" strategy as 
well as its policy of "strength" and put other non-socialist 
countries under its control by applying the American view of 
