<F P=104>  Pyongyang KCNA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Pyongyang, May 30 (KCNA) -- H.E. [His Exellency] 
Prince Chea Sim, acting head of state and president of the 
National Assembly of the Kingdom of Cambodia, H.R.H. [His Royal 
Highness] Prince Norodom Ranariddh, first prime minister, and 
