<H3> <TI>   DPRK Deputy Envoy on Statement </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    DPRK Deputy Envoy on Statement </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   SK3105072994 Seoul KBS-1 Radio Network in Korean 0700 GMT 31 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> SK3105072994 </F>
